%% User journey / lifecycle template
%% Replace placeholders with actual states and transitions.
flowchart LR
    START([Start]) --> STEP1[Step 1]
    STEP1 --> DECISION{Decision?}
    DECISION -->|yes| STEP2A[Step 2A]
    DECISION -->|no| STEP2B[Step 2B]
    STEP2A --> MERGE[Merge point]
    STEP2B --> MERGE
    MERGE --> CHECK{Check condition}
    CHECK -->|pass| SUCCESS([Done])
    CHECK -->|fail| SKIP([Skip / No-op])
